{{Short description|Mass stabbing in Villach, Austria}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2026}}
{{Infobox civilian attack
The attack took place at 15:33 on the Hauptplatz [[pedestrian zone]], located in the historic city center of Villach. A man began randomly stabbing pedestrians using a knife.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-02-15 |title=Austria: Villach knife attack leave teenager dead and four wounded |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cew5v48w54qo |access-date=2025-02-15 |website=BBC |language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Boy, 14, dies after five stabbed in Austria |url=https://news.sky.com/story/boy-14-dies-after-five-stabbed-in-austria-13310330 |access-date=2025-02-15 |website=Sky News |language=en}}</ref>
The attack was disrupted by the intervention of 42-year-old Alaaeddin Alhalabi,<ref>{{Cite web |last=Frischengruber |first=Kurt |date=2025-02-17 |title=Syrischer Essenslieferant wurde zum Helden |url=https://www.klick-kaernten.at/1236952025/syrischer-essenslieferant-wurde-zum-helden/ |access-date= |website=KLiCK Kärnten |language=de}}</ref> a Syrian [[Food delivery|food delivery worker]], who had seen two of the injured while driving past the scene and proceeded to ram the suspect, standing around three metres away,<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Hardegger |first=Angelika |date=2025-04-22 |title=Seit er einen Attentäter stoppte, ist er als «Held von Villach» berühmt |url=https://www.republik.ch/2025/04/22/seit-er-einen-attentaeter-stoppte-ist-er-als-held-von-villach-beruehmt |journal=Republik |language=de}}</ref> with his [[Volkswagen|VW]] car. The suspect was thrown back several metres, losing his knife and being lightly injured.<ref name=":6">{{Cite web |last=Kapellari |first=Jennifer |date=2025-02-16 |title="Versuchten ihn aufzuhalten und sahen das Messer" |url=https://www.krone.at/3692234 |access-date= |website=Kronen Zeitung |language=de}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web |last=Weber |first=Susi |date=2025-02-21 |title=Albtraum wird zur Realität: Ein Wangener erlebt den tödlichen Messerangriff von Villach mit |url=https://www.schwaebische.de/regional/allgaeu/wangen/zeuge-der-bluttat-von-villach-ich-suche-immer-noch-den-reset-knopf-3346063 |access-date=2025-10-23 |website=Schwäbische |language=de}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web |date=2025-02-16 |title=Tödliche Messerattacke in Villach: Tatverdächtiger lachte bei Festnahme |url=https://www.5min.at/5202502160629/toedliche-messerattacke-in-villach-tatverdaechtiger-lachte-bei-festnahme/ |access-date= |website=5 Minuten |language=de-AT}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-02-16 |title=Österreich: Jugendlicher bei islamistischem Anschlag getötet |url=https://www.faz.net/aktuell/politik/ausland/oesterreich-jugendlicher-bei-islamistischem-anschlag-getoetet-110299575.html |access-date= |website=FAZ.NET |language=de}}</ref> Alhalabi had intended to get out of his car and hold the suspect down, but bystanders began hitting the car, believing it to be another part of the attack. Alhalabi instead drove away

